The paper deals with modeling normative texts using a formalism, which involves natural language processing and rule-based extraction. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper also involves the development of an experimental aid, which could be relevant to Software Engineering (cs.SE).
